<COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">David Shaffer</COREF> was named to the new post of executive vice president of the Maxwell Macmillan group of this communications giant .
<COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">Mr. Shaffer</COREF> takes primary responsibility for the electronic and technical - services group .
<COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">He</COREF> had been group vice president of the electronic - publishing group .
Also , Sheldon Aboff , formerly a vice president at Maxwell , was named group vice president with responsibility for various electronic and publishing - group companies .
